  "Description": {
    "English": "The shell of a <span class=\"name name-special\">Sentinel drone</span>, all that remains after its destruction in combat. While the exterior is physically intact, its internals have been severely burned.<br><br>Given the right tools and several exotic components, it may be possible to <span class=\"name name-technology\">repair</span> it.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一台<span class=\"name name-special\">护卫无人机</span>的外壳，其余部分已经在战斗过程中被损毁。虽然外部相对完好，但内部结构已经彻底烧毁。<br><br>凭借合适的工具及异星构件，你也许能够<span class=\"name name-technology\">修复</span>这件设备。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">巡警無人機</span>的殼體，在戰鬥中被摧毀後僅存的元件。雖然外觀完好無損，其內部已被嚴重燒毀。<br><br>如果有正確的工具和幾個奇特元件，就有可能<span class=\"name name-technology\">修理</span>好。"
  },
